#{116}{}{What happened to Mark?}
{116}{}{马克怎么了？ -- What happened to Mark?}
#{117}{}{Well... I think I heard something about that, but I can't really remember anymore... Maybe you have something to refresh my memory... If you catch my drift.}
{117}{}{好。。。我想我听说了一些，但我已经记不起来了。。。也许你有什么东西可以让我记忆犹新。。。如果你明白我的意思。 -- Well... I think I heard something about that, but I can't really remember anymore... Maybe you have something to refresh my memory... If you catch my drift.}
#{118}{}{Of course, I understand. Would 100 bucks be enough?}
{118}{}{当然，我明白。100美元够吗？ -- Of course, I understand. Would 100 bucks be enough?}
