{119}{}{你知道我是谁还是我的老板？我想你最好不要这样。就说他从别人那里得到信息比我快得多吧。 -- Do you know who I am or who my boss is? I think it's best if you don't. Let's just say he gets information out of people much more quickly than me.}
#{120}{}{I know one trick I can perform on your fingers that might help. Want to find out?}
